-- Abu Dhabi Reports 6% Increase in Hotel Guests in August; 15% Rise in 2010
-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a
-- 2010-09-28T06:32:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/abu-dhabi-reports-6-increase-in-hotel-guests-in-august-15-rise-in-2010.html
The number of hotel guests in Abu
Dhabi, the capital of the United Arab Emirates, rose 6 percent
in August to 122,475.  In the first eight months of 2010 the sheikhdom recorded a
15 percent increase in hotel guests compared with the year-
earlier period, the Abu Dhabi Tourism Authority said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivian Salama in Abu Dhabi at 
 vsalama@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  